issue.title: Call to google url in GXP librarie
issue.body:
**Original author :** Van Hoecke Hélène 

To fix call to google url that should be made with https protocol instead of http one, some modificationes were made directly inside the GXP library code.
Better solution should be found to fix that.

comments.body:
**Original author :** Van Hoecke Hélène 

There will be no update on the GPX library so this issue can be closed.
